  <entry>
    <title>zsh主题</title>
    <link href="/2019/06/08/shell-zshTheme/"/>
    <url>/2019/06/08/shell-zshTheme/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>自己看起来很舒服的主题。当然是我自己没事改写的。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">local</span> resetColor=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%&#123;<span class="hljs-variable">$reset_color</span>%&#125;&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">local</span> cloud=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%&#123;<span class="hljs-variable">$fg_bold</span>[blue]%&#125;☁ <span class="hljs-variable">$resetColor</span>&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">local</span> dir=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%&#123;<span class="hljs-variable">$fg_bold</span>[green]%&#125;%c$resetColor<span class="hljs-variable">$resetColor</span>&quot;</span><br><br>PROMPT=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;$cloud $dir $(git_prompt_info)&#x27;</span><br><br>ZSH_THEME_GIT_PROMPT_PREFIX=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;↳%&#123;<span class="hljs-variable">$fg_bold</span>[blue]%&#125;&quot;</span><br>ZSH_THEME_GIT_PROMPT_SUFFIX=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$resetColor</span> &quot;</span><br>ZSH_THEME_GIT_PROMPT_DIRTY=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%&#123;<span class="hljs-variable">$fg_bold</span>[red]%&#125; ✘ &quot;</span><br>ZSH_THEME_GIT_PROMPT_CLEAN=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%&#123;<span class="hljs-variable">$fg_bold</span>[green]%&#125; ✔︎ &quot;</span><br><br>RPROMPT=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;[%*]&#x27;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
